{"content": "I need to multiply 320 \u00d7 843 in base 9.\n\n**Step 1: Convert to base 10**\n- 320\u2089 = 3\u00d79\u00b2 + 2\u00d79\u00b9 + 0\u00d79\u2070 = 3\u00d781 + 2\u00d79 + 0 = 243 + 18 + 0 = 261\u2081\u2080\n- 843\u2089 = 8\u00d79\u00b2 + 4\u00d79\u00b9 + 3\u00d79\u2070 = 8\u00d781 + 4\u00d79 + 3 = 648 + 36 + 3 = 687\u2081\u2080\n\n**Step 2: Multiply in base 10**\n- 261 \u00d7 687 = 179,307\u2081\u2080\n\n**Step 3: Convert result to base 9**\n- 179307 \u00f7 9 = 19923 r 0\n- 19923 \u00f7 9 = 2213 r 6\n- 2213 \u00f7 9 = 245 r 8\n- 245 \u00f7 9 = 27 r 2\n- 27 \u00f7 9 = 3 r 0\n- 3 \u00f7 9 = 0 r 3\n\nReading from bottom to top: **302860\u2089**\n\n302860", "model": "anthropic/claude-sonnet-4.5", "prompt_tokens": 827, "completion_tokens": 340}